a common enemy on the outside.

556
00:48:23,567 --> 00:48:24,860
Yun Chan-gyeong.

557
00:48:25,819 --> 00:48:27,404
I must see her immediately.

558
00:48:33,869 --> 00:48:38,540
So, you're saying I leaked
the video to the media?

559
00:48:39,124 --> 00:48:41,084
And broke my promise to you?

560
00:48:42,002 --> 00:48:43,295
You wanted

561
