576
00:49:30,592 --> 00:49:31,677
"Myung Hae Joon, bomber,

577
00:49:31,760 --> 00:49:34,096
bomber video,
Myung Hae Joon's whereabouts."

578
00:49:34,805 --> 00:49:37,432
The dismissal issue is completely gone.

579
00:49:37,516 --> 00:49:38,475
That's impressive.

