590
00:50:08,338 --> 00:50:09,297
You come with me.

591
00:50:09,923 --> 00:50:12,134
-After watching the video...
-Right now!

592
00:50:12,217 --> 00:50:14,636
in which Myung Hae Joon claims
to be the bomber,

593
00:50:15,220 --> 00:50:17,055
people have been voicing
their fear and anxiety,

594
