or a controversy,

603
00:50:49,671 --> 00:50:51,548
nothing can beat it.

604
00:50:53,925 --> 00:50:57,179
I'm jealous you have such a good staff.

605
00:50:59,014 --> 00:51:01,725
Secretary Han isn't at the Blue House
anymore,

606
