Yes, but let's make the questions
easy and clear.

613
00:51:26,458 --> 00:51:28,585
That's better for setting up
positive answers.

614
00:51:28,668 --> 00:51:29,836
-Okay.
-Good.

615
00:51:30,921 --> 00:51:31,880
Mr. President.

616
00:51:34,216 --> 00:51:35,842
You don't have to worry.

617
00:51:37,135 --> 00:51:39,513
If the approval rating rises
in the public survey,

618
00:51:40,055 --> 00:51:42,974
your dismissal issue won't hinder
government operations any longer.

619
00:51:44,601 --> 00:51:45,477
Is that why...

620
00:51:47,646 --> 00:51:49,147
you leaked the video?

621
00:51:56,863 --> 00:51:58,198
I was on my way to tell you.

622
00:52:10,961 --> 00:52:12,170
Please get back to work.

623
00:52:30,188 --> 00:52:32,566
Myung Hae Joon's video was classified.

624
00:52:34,776 --> 00:52:37,028
You leaked that to the public

625
00:52:37,112 --> 00:52:38,405
without telling anyone

626
