or getting permission.

627
00:52:43,076 --> 00:52:45,078
Is putting national security in danger

628
00:52:46,454 --> 00:52:48,039
part of your political choice?

629
00:52:50,834 --> 00:52:52,752
You can punish me

630
00:52:54,379 --> 00:52:57,507
for leaking a state secret
or public endangerment by causing havoc.

631
00:52:58,675 --> 00:53:01,344
-Then why did you do this?
-It was to protect you!

632
00:53:03,221 --> 00:53:04,806
General Lee

633
00:53:05,098 --> 00:53:08,018
will be willing to fight Cambodia
to catch Myung Hae Joon.

634
00:53:08,101 --> 00:53:10,812
He doesn't approve of you
as Commander-in-Chief.

635
00:53:10,896 --> 00:53:13,315
This is the price for your honesty.

636
00:53:17,944 --> 00:53:20,655
Do you know why you admitted
that you were dismissed?

637
00:53:22,365 --> 00:53:25,535
You wanted to prove
you don't have any desire for power

638
00:53:25,619 --> 00:53:28,246
and that you're a good person
unlike other politicians.

639
00:53:29,581 --> 00:53:32,709
You're being stubborn and trying
to fight with your bare hands

640
00:53:32,792 --> 00:53:35,503
on the battlefield because you're scared
you'll get your sword bloody.

641
00:53:35,587 --> 00:53:36,922
There can be two outcomes.

642
00:53:37,005 --> 00:53:38,965
You either die bleeding or surrendering.

643
00:53:44,763 --> 00:53:45,639
I...

644
00:53:49,851 --> 00:53:52,354
don't want to fight
under a commander like that anymore.

645
00:53:58,401 --> 00:53:59,861
I want to win.

646
00:54:03,198 --> 00:54:05,116
LETTER OF RESIGNATION

