and some 200 people were victims
of this tragedy.

662
00:55:37,042 --> 00:55:38,209
Not only that,

663
00:55:40,712 --> 00:55:44,507
he sent a video to the Blue House
to mock us.

664
00:55:45,216 --> 00:55:47,343
Since the video was leaked,

665
00:55:47,427 --> 00:55:50,305
our people are suffering
in fear and anxiety.

666
00:55:51,473 --> 00:55:54,059
It is the duty of a sovereign state

667
00:55:54,142 --> 00:55:56,853
to catch Myung Hae Joon and punish him.

668
00:55:59,272 --> 00:56:03,818
I won't hand Myung Hae Joon
over to North Korea easily.

669
00:56:03,902 --> 00:56:05,987
A diplomatic dispute with Cambodia

670
00:56:06,988 --> 00:56:08,990
will bring greater anxiety and fear.

671
00:56:09,074 --> 00:56:12,410
