suppressed with force.

676
00:56:30,011 --> 00:56:31,513
President Park,

677
00:56:32,138 --> 00:56:34,557
you should use power if you have it...

678
00:56:37,393 --> 00:56:39,395
without hesitating or wavering.

679
00:57:03,503 --> 00:57:05,046
You're right, General Lee.

680
00:57:12,053 --> 00:57:15,140
I'll use my power since I have it
without hesitating or wavering.

681
