I am revoking your military authority.

682
00:57:32,699 --> 00:57:35,994
General Lee Gwan-muk,
you are relieved of your post.

683
00:57:40,373 --> 00:57:41,332
As of now,

684
00:57:42,125 --> 00:57:45,920
anyone who gives orders to the military
without my permission...

685
00:57:48,923 --> 00:57:51,384
will be punished
for conspiring to start a rebellion.

686
00:57:54,429 --> 00:57:55,597
There will be...

687
00:58:04,397 --> 00:58:05,440
no exceptions.

