739
01:03:29,764 --> 01:03:30,681
Congratulations,

740
01:03:32,099 --> 01:03:34,143
Chief Presidential Secretary
Cha Yeong-jin.

741
01:03:41,025 --> 01:03:43,194
Wait, Ms. Jeong.

742
01:03:50,368 --> 01:03:51,744
Well...

743
01:03:54,080 --> 01:03:55,623
